snippet.title: Gedda Cake - Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the oficial first demo trailer for Gedda Cake, a 2D action-platformer about Dragons and Cakes.

Wishlist Gedda Cake on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1785630/Gedda_Cake/

Follow us on Twitter for development updates:
https://twitter.com/GeddaCake
